Clevite Industries Inc said itagreed in principle to form a joint venture company withBridgestone Corp of Tokyo.    Based in Milan, Ohio, the joint venture company,Clevite-Bridgestone Co, will manufacture and sellrubber-to-metal products for the automotive industry in theUnited States, Canada and Mexico.    Initially, it said the new company will manufactureproducts in Clevite's existing Angola, Ind. plant. Reuter&#3;